♪I've been tracing back♪

2
00:00:16,700 --> 00:00:20,540
♪Went through all the sweetness and sorrow♪

3
00:00:20,620 --> 00:00:24,180
♪Chasing a dream till it starts♪

4
00:00:24,220 --> 00:00:27,060
♪All the subtle things♪

5
