377
00:14:55,560 --> 00:14:56,599
Do you really want to know why?

378
00:14:56,599 --> 00:14:57,800
Let me tell you.

379
00:14:58,400 --> 00:14:59,479
It's because there aren't many

380
00:14:59,479 --> 00:15:01,680
