418
00:16:39,800 --> 00:16:41,400
You don't have to worry
about other things.

419
00:16:45,080 --> 00:16:45,759
Father.

420
00:16:47,719 --> 00:16:48,359
Father.

421
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:50,680
